Package: ggtextures
Title: Drawing Textured Rectangles and Bars with grid and ggplot2
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Claus",
           family = "Wilke",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "wilke@austin.utexas.edu")
Description: This package provides functions and geoms to draw textured rectangles and
  bars with the grid graphics system and with ggplot2. This enables both bar graphs with
  pattern fill and isotype bar graphs.
